strings: <voice_0x01001899><se_low>King of tricks: Well, yeah...honestly, now I know what you're talking about with King Kravis.
<voice_0x0100189A><se_low>King of tricks: Now I understand your feelings. This royal reunion has been in the planning for years.
<voice_0x0100189B><se_low>King of tricks: I fear you talk too much about this. different for you
<voice_0x0100189C><se_low>King of tricks: No need to worry! I am sorry, my king. We're going to the tavern.
